  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要一个时间轴来展示页面发布的完整生命周期，从草稿到最终发布。核心系统是基于HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine的，所以得把这个引擎名放进去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Page Publish Lifecycle",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "Drafting",
        "Published"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那生命周期分几个阶段？我初步想分成草稿、调度和已发布三个阶段，每个阶段有关键动作。比如草稿阶段，页面刚创建时published_at应该是nil，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Drafting",
        "Create page",
        "published_at is nil"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，草稿阶段published_at是nil。另外还要体现内容是怎么加进去的——我们是通过content_page_blocks来添加内容区块的，这个关联关系要画出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Add content blocks",
        "content_page_blocks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，草稿阶段我放两个节点：创建页面（published_at为nil）和添加内容区块（通过content_page_blocks）。接下来是调度阶段，设置published_at为now就变成scheduled状态，同时更新隐私、布局和slug时会触发缓存键更新，包括updated_at。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scheduling",
        "Set published_at now",
        "scheduled",
        "Update privacy/layout/slug",
        "cached keys include updated_at"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "缓存键的部分表述再精确一点——是cached keys include updated_at，不是只更新updated_at。然后是最终发布阶段，published_at小于等于当前时间就视为已发布。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cached keys include updated_at",
        "Published",
        "published_at <= now"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我调整一下调度阶段的描述，确保是cached keys include updated_at。那发布后的可见性逻辑呢？需要体现权限判断吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cached keys include updated_at"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要。可见性取决于policy allows，具体是privacy为public或者用户经过authorized授权才能看到。这个条件判断要放在已发布阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Visible if policy allows",
        "privacy public",
        "authorized"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完整结构确认了：标题Page Publish Lifecycle，三个阶段Drafting、Scheduling、Published，每个阶段的关键节点和条件都涵盖。HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine标注在创建页面节点，可见性逻辑用policy allows判断。我这就定稿。",
